# Design Harness (Cursor)

For **full pages, landing sites, marketing pages, or any UI shipping**, follow the installed skill (default path **`~/.claude/skills/design-harness/`**):

1. **`SKILL.md`** — full 4-layer system

## Quick Reference

### Before Writing JSX
- Lock **font pairing** (display + body) and **delight budget** (1 hero, 1 mid-page max)
- Typography is 60% of "premium" — fix fonts and spacing before any motion

### Design Skills (install these)
- **Impeccable** (impeccable.style) — `/audit`, `/polish`, `/delight`. Run `/audit` before every ship.
- **Emil Kowalski** (emilkowal.ski/skill) — animations and UI polish from Linear/Vercel
- **Interface Design** (interface-design.dev) — persistent design specs between sessions
- **Northstone App UI** (github.com/Jacknelson6/northstone-app-ui) — Shadcn + Bedrock pipeline

### Agent Canvases
- **Paper** (paper.design) — HTML/CSS-native, MCP tools, design-as-code
- **Pencil** (pencil.dev) — Git-diffable .pen format, agent swarm mode

### Implementation Rules
- **Shadcn blocks first** for skeleton (`npx shadcn@latest add <block>`)
- **One visual system** across sections (same radius, borders, button weight)
- **Motion is seasoning**: at most 1 ambient background (hero/footer only)
- **No magnetic hovers** (Magnet/MagnetLines) — hard ban
- **Ring technique** over solid borders: `ring-1 ring-gray-950/10 shadow-md`
- **Neutral grays**, not slate/zinc
- Use `motion/react` not `framer-motion`
- `'use client'` on motion leaves, `dynamic()` for WebGL

### Delight Budget
| 1× hero | Typographic treatment, SplitText, single ambient bg, or asymmetric layout |
| 1× mid-page | Scroll reveal on ONE section or gentle fade-in |
| 1× footer | Logo loop, marquee, quiet motion |
| BANNED | Multiple WebGL + parallax + grain + sparkles + gradient text stacking |

### Shipping Checklist
```
0   — Scope (marketing vs dashboard vs auth)
0.5 — Design lock (fonts, delight budget, what stays calm)
1   — Skeleton (Shadcn blocks, scaffold routes)
2   — Tokens (project design system / CSS variables)
3   — Motion pass (1 hero moment + 1 optional mid-page)
3.5 — Cohesion (strip weakest effect if >2 "wow", unify radii)
4   — Content & assets (real copy, next/image, metadata)
5   — Verify (build + lint + dev smoke)
```

### Before Ship Checks
- [ ] One sentence: audience + promise?
- [ ] One focal point above the fold?
- [ ] More than 2 special effects? Remove the weakest.
- [ ] Mobile simplifies?
- [ ] Looks good WITHOUT animation?

